OL,3,CJewish staff 'suffer in silence',
OL,4,Caccording to NHS antisemitism review
OL,6,FSome Jewish patients and staff in the
OL,7,FNHS feel the need to hide their
OL,8,Freligious identity and "suffer in
OL,9,Fsilence", the head of a review into
OL,10,Fantisemitism and other forms of racism
OL,11,Fin the health service has said.
OL,13,FLord John Mann, who was tasked last
OL,14,Fyear with looking into the issue by
OL,15,Fthe prime minister, called on the NHS
OL,16,Fto be "a responsible and inclusive
OL,17,Femployer".
OL,26,@pD@XOUqD@HO]xD@GOUyD@IO]
