PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780611062
OL,3,CJewish staff 'suffer in silence',
OL,4,Caccording to NHS antisemitism review
OL,6,FThe Department of Health and Social
OL,7,FCare (DHSC) said Lord Mann's review
OL,8,Fheard how some Jewish staff in the NHS
OL,9,Fexperience "routine ostracism" with
OL,10,Fsome even considering leaving the
OL,11,Fhealth service.
OL,13,FThe report is also expected to say
OL,14,Fthat some Jewish patients reported not
OL,15,Fwanting to present to the NHS for
OL,16,Ftreatment or putting off receiving
OL,17,Fimportant care, amid concerns around
OL,18,Fantisemitism.
OL,26,@qD@LOUqD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
