OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780611062
OL,3,CJewish staff 'suffer in silence',
OL,4,Caccording to NHS antisemitism review
OL,6,FThe government said reforms it now
OL,7,Fintends to make in light of the review
OL,8,Fwill "will benefit everyone who
OL,9,Fexperiences hatred or abuse in the
OL,10,Fhealth service", not just victims of
OL,11,Fantisemitism.
OL,26,@pD@FOUrD@OO]
