CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780611062
OL,3,CJewish staff 'suffer in silence',
OL,4,Caccording to NHS antisemitism review
OL,6,FDHSC said a new staff standard will be
OL,7,Fput in place, setting minimum
OL,8,Fexpectations for how organisations
OL,9,Fmust prevent, respond to, and learn
OL,10,Ffrom incidents of racism, while
OL,11,Fmandatory anti-racism training,
OL,12,Fspecifically including antisemitism,
OL,13,Fwill be rolled out for NHS trust
OL,14,Fchairs and chief executives within six
OL,15,Fmonths.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
