FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780611062
OL,3,CJewish staff 'suffer in silence',
OL,4,Caccording to NHS antisemitism review
OL,6,FMandatory training on equality,
OL,7,Fdiversity and human rights, which is
OL,8,Falready in place for 1.5 million
OL,9,Fstaff, will be updated to include
OL,10,F"quality-assured content" on
OL,11,Fantisemitism and anti-Muslim
OL,12,Fhostility, the department added.
OL,14,FThe government is also committing to
OL,15,Fsetting out a single set of national
OL,16,Fguidance for employers, which would
OL,17,Fclearly define their responsibilities
OL,18,Fin tackling discrimination and give
OL,19,Fguidance and examples of what kinds of
OL,20,Fincidents might need to be referred to
OL,21,Fthe regulator.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@YO]
