PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780611062
OL,3,CJewish staff 'suffer in silence',
OL,4,Caccording to NHS antisemitism review
OL,6,FLord Mann said: "Jewish people have to
OL,7,Fbe confident that they will receive
OL,8,Fthe same treatment as everyone else,
OL,9,Fat all times in all situations.
OL,11,F"If people feel, as they do, that some
OL,12,Fhave to hide their identity as
OL,13,Fpatients or suffer in silence as
OL,14,Fstaff, then the universality of the
OL,15,FNHS is fundamentally breached.
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,26,@nD@QOUsD@AOU
