PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780611062
OL,3,CJewish staff 'suffer in silence',
OL,4,Caccording to NHS antisemitism review
OL,6,F"The NHS as an employer must act as a
OL,7,Fresponsible and inclusive employer and
OL,8,Ftake the responsibility of making its
OL,9,Femployment and service to patients one
OL,10,Fthat the entirety of the country,
OL,11,Fincluding our Jewish community, can
OL,12,Ffeel and see is one that is for them
OL,13,Fas well as everybody else."
OL,15,FHealth Secretary James Murray said
OL,16,Fracism and discrimination "betray
OL,17,Feverything the NHS stands for and its
OL,18,Fability to provide safe, world-class
OL,19,Fcare".
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@[O]xD@[OU{D@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
