SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780611062
OL,3,CJewish staff 'suffer in silence',
OL,4,Caccording to NHS antisemitism review
OL,6,FDean Royles, interim chief executive
OL,7,Fof NHS Employers, said the review
OL,8,F"reveals beyond any doubt that
OL,9,Fantisemitism and other forms of racism
OL,10,Fin the NHS are rising, as they are
OL,11,Fwithin our wider society, and must be
OL,12,Ftackled with urgency by all of us".
OL,26,@pD@AOUtD@bO]
